## ðŸŒ Featured Projects

### ðŸ¨ [Global Hotel Review Analysis (2015â€“2017)](./Hotel%20Review%20Analysis)
**Tools:** Python, R, Tableau  
**Focus:** Text sentiment analysis & KPI-driven dashboard design  

- Analyzed **515K+ hotel reviews** to uncover how ratings differ by nationality and traveler type.  
- Performed **sentiment scoring** with VADER and validated group differences using ANOVA in R.  
- Built an interactive Tableau dashboard showing:
  - KPI cards (Avg Rating, Sentiment, Total Reviews, % Positive)
  - Top 10 Reviewer Nationalities by Rating
  - Sentiment by Traveler Type
  - Yearly Rating Trend (2015â€“2017)
  - World Map by Rating  
- ðŸ“ˆ *Outcome:* Identified that **Couples gave the highest positive sentiment (52%)**, while **Business travelers rated lowest (~7.9â€“8.0)**.  

ðŸ“„ [View Project Files â†’](./Hotel%20Review%20Analysis)

